    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "Older poor-condition example being sold honestly as-is. This car is not a clean driver and should be expected to have significant cosmetic wear, paint and body flaws, a worn interior, and likely deferred maintenance or mechanical needs before it can be considered dependable. It may still run and drive, but buyers should come expecting a project, a budget fixer-upper, or a parts/restoration candidate rather than a sorted vehicle. Best suited for someone who understands what a poor-condition car entails and is comfortable taking on needed repairs.",
