    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Budget-friendly and ready for its next owner, this vehicle offers a practical way into reliable transportation at an accessible price. It shows its age cosmetically and is best suited for someone seeking straightforward value, a work commuter, or a project opportunity. If you want an honest car with plenty of usefulness left and room to make it your own, this is a compelling choice.",
