      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Looking for a cheap set of wheels that gets the job done? This car isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s an honest little runner with plenty of usefulness left for someone who needs dependable basic transport, a backup vehicle, or a project to tinker with. It\u2019s priced to be affordable, and with the right owner, it could still serve well. If you want something budget-friendly without the fancy price tag, this one\u2019s worth a look.",
